---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="success-page">
		<div class="success-card">
			<div class="icon-wrapper">
				<svg class="success-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
					<path d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
				</svg>
			</div>
			
			<h1>¡Gracias por tu compra!</h1>
			<p class="message">Tu pago se ha procesado correctamente. Haz clic en el botón de abajo para obtener tu Pack Completo de Prompts.</p>
			
			<div class="download-section">
				<!-- El atributo download fuerza al navegador a descargar el archivo en lugar de solo abrirlo -->
				<a href="/descargas/pack-prompts-solene.pdf" download="Pack-Prompts-Solene.pdf" class="btn primary download-btn">
					<svg class="btn-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21 18.75V16.5M16.5 12 12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
					</svg>
					Descargar PDF Ahora
				</a>
			</div>
			
			<p class="note">¿Tuviste algún problema con la descarga? <a href="https://wa.me/18438226879" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Contáctanos por WhatsApp</a> y te lo enviaremos manualmente.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.success-page {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		min-height: 60vh;
		padding: 2rem 1rem;
	}

	.success-card {
		background: var(--blanco-editorial);
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--pizarra-profunda) 15%, transparent);
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		max-width: 500px;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -15px color-mix(in srgb, var(--pizarra-profunda) 20%, transparent);
	}

	.icon-wrapper {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 4rem;
		height: 4rem;
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--oro-kodak) 20%, transparent);
		color: var(--oro-kodak);
		border-radius: 50%;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.success-icon {
		width: 2.5rem;
		height: 2.5rem;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
	}

	.message {
		margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--carbon-cinematografico);
	}

	.download-section .btn {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		display: inline-flex;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.btn-icon {
		width: 1.25rem;
		height: 1.25rem;
	}

	.note {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--carbon-cinematografico) 70%, transparent);
	}

	/* Use global link styles from Layout.astro */
	.note a {
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	/* Buttons are styled via global .btn classes */
	.btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		text-decoration: none;
		padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-weight: 700;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease;
		font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
	}
	
	.btn:hover {
		transform: scale(1.03);
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--oro-kodak);
		color: var(--carbon-cinematografico);
	}
</style>